org.codice.ddf.notifications.store

Class PersistentNotification

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.HashMap<String,String>
        • org.codice.ddf.notifications.store.PersistentNotification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,String>

    public class PersistentNotification
extends HashMap<String,String>
    Serializable Notification that is persisted to disk by @FileSystemPersistenceProvider and includes the unique ID generated as the cache key for the notification.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
